==Abstract==

This TVS proposes a scheme for adding Replay Protection.

==Motivation==

Stop replaying of Bitcoin Cash transactions on Bitcoin Clashic blockchain.

Reduce unintended spamming on Bitcoin Clashic blockchain.

Reduce loss of Bitcoin Clashic for Bitcoin Cash senders.

Eliminate gain of Bitcoin Clashic to recipients of replayed trasactons.

==Rationale==

Bitcoin Cash transactors are inadvertantly sending Bitcoin Clashic when sending Bitcoin Cash.

Exchanges requiring Replay Protection before listing $BCL/$BCHC

==Deployment==

This TVS will be deployed by Block Height and Bitcoin Clashic ABCD client version.


